; Regression test for issue #739: prices/pricedb only show pricedb info for
; commodities listed in transactions (BZ#739)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/739
;
; The `prices` and `pricedb` commands should report price history for every
; commodity that has a P directive, not only those that are referenced by
; some posting in the journal.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 GOOG $100.00

2024/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments     10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test prices
2024/01/01 AAPL          $150.00
2024/01/01 GOOG          $100.00
end test

test pricedb
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 GOOG $100.00
end test
